trans-unit.source: Represents the method that will handle the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded"></xref> event, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted"></xref> event, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed"></xref> event, <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved"></xref> event, or <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged"></xref> event of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: 처리 하는 메서드를 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded"> </xref> 이벤트를 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted"> </xref> 이벤트를 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed"> </xref> 이벤트를 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved"> </xref> 이벤트 또는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged"> </xref> 의 이벤트는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager"> </xref> 개체입니다.

trans-unit.source: The method specified in the WebPartEventHandler delegate will be called when a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded> event, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted> event, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed> event, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved> event, or <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged> event is raised.
trans-unit.target: WebPartEventHandler 대리자에 지정 된 메서드가 때 호출 됩니다는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>이벤트, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted>이벤트를 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed>이벤트를 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved>이벤트 또는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged>이벤트가 발생 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.SelectedWebPartChanged> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartMoved> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartClosed> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartDeleted> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.WebPartAdded>

trans-unit.source: Page developers can provide custom handlers for Web Parts events by adding an `OnWebPartAdded` attribute, `OnWebPartDeleted` attribute, `OnWebPartClosed` attribute, `OnWebPartMoved` attribute, or `OnSelectedWebPartChanged` attribute to the `<asp:webpartmanager>` element in a page, and assigning a custom method name to the attribute.
trans-unit.target: 페이지 개발자가 추가 하 여 웹 파트 이벤트에 대 한 사용자 지정 처리기를 제공할 수 있습니다는 `OnWebPartAdded` 특성 `OnWebPartDeleted` 특성을 `OnWebPartClosed` 특성 `OnWebPartMoved` 특성 또는 `OnSelectedWebPartChanged` 특성을 `<asp:webpartmanager>` 의 요소는 페이지 및 사용자 지정 메서드 이름 특성에 할당 합니다.

trans-unit.source: A custom handler can also be assigned programmatically.
trans-unit.target: 사용자 지정 처리기를 프로그래밍 방식으로 할당할 수도 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: For more information on programmatically assigning an event handler, see [NIB: How to: Connect Event Handler Methods to Events](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/348e9600-22e3-49a2-8864-11c5bb3e98fc).
trans-unit.target: 프로그래밍 방식으로 이벤트 처리기를 할당에 대 한 자세한 내용은 참조 하십시오. [NIB: 방법: 이벤트에 이벤트 처리기 메서드에 연결](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/348e9600-22e3-49a2-8864-11c5bb3e98fc)합니다.
